f the fish? (7marks) <br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母！"},{"pid":"16b46bcbc7954528848b3c0e5bb55fb78ac3a600","tid":2507480,"uid":385628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"楊修之死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42e5326c8d6e75b7d15c7280fb70d6f61b70695","tid":2507480,"uid":73406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"天亮了，我要起床上學去。"},{"pid":"7c1746be662e14b4d82e40802e37e0a62034e51e","tid":2507480,"uid":377331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:14:42.000Z","msg":"岳陽樓記"},{"pid":"06837bbb8d3c04f96ff3632f280464be5e8d758d","tid":2507480,"uid":44007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"燕詩<br />\n當你覺得被仔女遺棄個陣 當年其實你都係咁對父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617c24fe956553592ca6571fbe09b9b0a10073b6","tid":2507480,"uid":85516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"六國破滅，非兵不利，戰不善，弊在賂秦。"},{"pid":"b1163f716ddf2f36fb7b3ae0aa49fc99aab0870e","tid":2507480,"uid":26385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5bc2a722197de505c67765312038a28b4e020511","tid":2507480,"uid":314767,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:31:11.000Z","msg":"差不多先生傳<br />\n依篇係自讀篇章嚟 細個睇完勁鍾意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:16:46.000Z","msg":"孔乙己同差不多先生真係好正<br />\n好準確咁描繪咗中國人嘅迂腐同做野求撚其心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n解釋埋點解中國人咁多年嚟都係咁撚失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n百幾年前嘅文章放返現今社會一樣啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1c787adb73fa2d06a977f9a73bd9255a8b5682","tid":2507480,"uid":3195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:21:59.000Z","msg":"記得幾篇文言文，<br />\n一篇係習慣說，一篇係為學一首示子侄，仲有一篇係燕詩。<br />\n燕詩最尾一段係咁：<br />\n「燕燕爾勿悲，爾當反自思。<br />\n思爾爲雛日，高飛背母時。<br />\n當時父母念，今日爾應知。」<br />\n燕詩原意應該係寫啲人忘記父母養育之恩，<br />\n想話人不孝唔應該個啲<br />\n我睇完係覺得，<br />\n大自然就係咁，<br />\n做咩要強加你人類套道德落啲雀到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022b311890bbff9879ab1064aa784331fe69176a","tid":2507480,"uid":46823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7092a95e4e88cbabd42a137da3f72994c4f7b077","tid":2507480,"uid":136800,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:34:16.000Z","msg":"桃花園記"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:32:35.000Z","msg":"嗰陣覺得好奇幻但又有啲懸疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b240971f1c20238a455b68b2f6cdbdf5dce5184","tid":2507480,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"六國論<br />\n到依家都久唔久睇翻<br />\n<br />\n有冇唔太深既古文介紹？"},{"pid":"bfd3f33a00d6d63155e5d1a6226603f5912975eb","tid":2507480,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49cb83a59d90c4559f71804c7c6e496bf78bd052","tid":2507480,"uid":133183,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:58:52.000Z","msg":"今日割五城，明日割十城，然後得一夕安寢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"呢篇真係好深刻，深刻到依家仲會睇翻"},{"pid":"43ff8c9105408677fc302cd883fdb6aeda9357e8","tid":2507480,"uid":101554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T15:17:10.000Z","msg":"出師未捷身先死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07fc08b4bee8d5a46016c34755520357d0bf7d57","tid":2507480,"uid":73406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b240971f1c20238a455b68b2f6cdbdf5dce5184","tid":2507480,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"六國論<br />\n到依家都久唔久睇翻<br />\n<br />\n有冇唔太深既古文介紹？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T16